attributionInfo.brokerName: Southern Homes of the Carolinas, Inc

data.description:
Welcome home! This beautiful brick, 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is ready for its new owner(s). No HOA, so you can make this place truly yours. All reasonable offers will be considered! A big plus is that there's a fenced yard for some extra privacy. 

There is ample storage, and you won't run out of parking! The best part? Location...It's close to downtown Charlotte, Charlotte Douglas International Airport, Whitewater Center, and major highways. Schedule your showing!
